arts.ttl: Sublime PSV Eindhoven put six goals past FC Twente
arts.sum: PSV Eindhoven came from behind to hammer FC Twente 6-1 on Friday evening. FC Twente took a surprise lead in the tenth minute when in-form Sam Steijn found the net with an outstanding strike from distance. PSV equalised ten minutes later when Noa Lang beat Michal Sadilek before firing into the far corner.
